OL,3,CIs it time for outdated parliamentary
OL,4,Clanguage to 'give way'?
OL,6,FLucy Powell, Leader of the House of
OL,7,FCommons and chair of the committee,
OL,8,Fsaid its mission is to "close the gap
OL,9,Fbetween Parliament and the public" by
OL,10,F"finding ways to make the work of the
OL,11,FHouse of Commons simpler and easier to
OL,12,Funderstand".
OL,14,FShe added: "It's time for us to lead
OL,15,Ffrom the front and make the physical
OL,16,Fparliamentary estate, as well as the
OL,17,Flanguage and procedures used to
OL,18,Fexplain what's happening, as
OL,19,Faccessible as possible."
